<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Page not found on our site. Check out the best flowers for delivery today!">
    <meta name="keywords" content="404, page not found, flowers, delivery, same-day flowers, best flowers for mom">
    <title>Oops! Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            color: #FF2E63;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #555;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background-color: #FF2E63;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #E02456;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <h2>Oops! We can't find the page you're looking for.</h2>
    <p>
        It seems the page you were trying to reach does not exist or has been moved. But don't worry! You can still find amazing flowers for any occasion, including same-day delivery options.
    </p>
    <a href="https://www.floristone.com/main.cfm?occ=sd&source_id=aff&AffiliateID=2013017799" class="cta-button" target="_blank">Shop Same-Day Flowers Now</a>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Send Flowers Online. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
